body.name: Ring Doorbell Wireless Doorbell Chime V5, V6 and V7,Ring Doorbell Chime Inside House
features: 🔔【WIRE-FREE CONVENIENCE】: The Door Chime is 100% wire-free, which allows you to place it up to 80 feet away from the Wireless Video Doorbell. You can hear the ring from anywhere in or around your house thanks to the doorbell chime.

🔔【REAL-TIME ALERTS】: Stay updated with our ring doorbell chime inside house. The Doorbell Chime ensures you receive alerts inside or outside your home whenever someone rings your Video Doorbell. You can place the doorbell chime in the living room or by the pool to ensure you never miss a visitor.

🔔【EASY PAIRING】: Pairing your ring doorbell wireless with the chime is a piece of cake. It works seamlessly with video doorbell models V5, V6, and V7, and it might also work with other models using 433MHz RF transmissions (Check with your device maker).

🔔【NO BATTERY, NO FUSS】: Our ring doorbell chime inside house doesn't require any batteries. Simply plug it into a wall outlet to extend the ringer from the video doorbell. No more worrying about battery replacements with this doorbell chime.

🔔【CUSTOMIZABLE RINGTONES】: The ring doorbell wireless chime offers 52 unique ringtones to choose from, with 4 different volume levels. With a maximum working range of 600ft and the ability to transmit through walls, you can adjust the sound and volume to your ideal setting with this doorbell chime.
body.description: NOTES:This wireless chime works with wireless video doorbell model V5, V6 and V7. Please ask the device maker if they are compatible with 433MHz RF receiver. PLEASE READ CAREFULLY:It does NOT work with Ring video doorbell. Specifications:Sound: 52 ringtones Range: 600ft(180m) Ideal Volume: 4 levels Voltage: 90-250V Frequency: 433MHz (+/- 200KHz) Instructions to pair: Setup your video doorbell V5 first, and power on the V5 doorbell; Press and hold the volume button on the chime for 3 seconds until the LED indicator lights up, the chime will enter into paring status;Press the ring button on the V5 doorbell within 5 seconds after step 2. The pairing is complete once the LED indicator on the chime is blinking.√How to select different music for chime ringtone? Press up or down to select the desired ringtone;If you would like to switch, hold the top volume key for 3 seconds until the blue LED lights up constantly without blinking; Immediately press the ring button on the wireless video doorbell, the new ringtone is set when you see the blue LED blinks. √How to unpair or clear the pairing? To clean the pairing, unplug from the wall power outlet first, then hold the top volume key while plug into the wall outlet again, hold for another ten seconds as the blue LED lights up constantly without blinking. √How to change the volume? There are four volume levels, press and top volume key and repeat to circle the volume levels until you are satisfied.
